modName: Remodeled Armors FIXED and pantyless - UNP version
summary:
The remodeled armor by asianboy345 with the steel armor plate and dwarven armor striping error fixed, as well as pantyless.
Original models by Mak07 for CBBEv3M, UNP version by asianboy345
Original for CBBE: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13004
UNP versions: http://http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19772
descriptionHtml:
This is the remodeled armor pack for UNP by asianboy 345 with the striping error on the Steel Plate armor and Dwarven armor fixed. Also includes a pantyless version of the mod.
Original models by Mak07 for CBBEv3M, UNP version by asianboy345
Original for CBBE: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13004
UNP versions: http://http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19772

Any questions, concerns or tips are appreciated.
